      "value": "<blockquote><p>Prerequisite: Level 5+ Warlock, Pact of the Blade invocation</p></blockquote><p>Once per turn when you hit a creature with your pact weapon, you can expend a Pact Magic spell slot to deal an extra 1d8 Force damage to the target, plus another 1d8 per level of the spell slot, and you can give the target the &amp;Reference[Prone] condition if it is Huge or smaller.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-AO8GTueywc2Doff2\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Smite</strong> activity consumes a Pact Magic spell slot and increases the damage based on your pact spell level.</p></section>",
